@$OpenBSD$
- OpenBSD doesn't need libdl
- use pkg-config to find glib libs
- make sure libcamlrun.a is writable after copying it from system libs
- don't attempt to overwrite an optimized library with a non-existant one
- fix .pc datarootdir
